  "detailed_description": "<h1>Upcoming games</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394800/extras/1c29f0f201e8e83a05426e00873aa132.poster.avif?t=1671867284\" width=500 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394800/extras/1c29f0f201e8e83a05426e00873aa132.webm?t=1671867284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394800/extras/1c29f0f201e8e83a05426e00873aa132.mp4?t=1671867284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This is a role-playing plot plus level decryption game.<br>On the surface, Mr. Wang is an enthusiastic apartment repairman, who likes to help female neighbors solve small problems in life, but behind the scenes, Lao Wang is an asshole and likes cuckolds. In the plot, Pharaoh will spy on the neighbors’ privacy while repairing the neighbors, and constantly approach the female neighbors through despicable means.<br>If you are interested in Lao Wang's story, please don't miss it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394800/extras/b26fcf2d8b9f29b42fe474d2f5dafdbc.poster.avif?t=1671867284\" width=500 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394800/extras/b26fcf2d8b9f29b42fe474d2f5dafdbc.webm?t=1671867284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394800/extras/b26fcf2d8b9f29b42fe474d2f5dafdbc.mp4?t=1671867284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game operation is simple, the plot is interesting.<br>The game contains multiple endings.<br><br>Other game series recommended by the developer:<br>SeeKgirl Ⅰ-Ⅵ ，SeeKgirl FOG:Ⅰ，Lost，Taboos: Cracks",
